    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the S54B32 inline-six power plant. The engine exhibits flawless compression and operates with surgical precision thanks to its individual throttle bodies and a fully serviced Double VANOS system. Power is channeled through a Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential, providing exceptional tactile feedback. The chassis has been meticulously maintained, with a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings ensuring the original torsional rigidity remains intact. Every mechanical component, from the cross-drilled rotors to the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension, is in peak operational condition, free of the common fatigue points associated with the E46 platform. This is a turn-key, collector-grade vehicle for the purist who demands mechanical transparency.",
